==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: PROLOG
<hw>PRO"LOG</hw> <pr>(pr⟦omac⟧"l⟦ocr⟧g)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Computers)</fld> <def>A declarative higher-level programming
language in which instructions are written not as explicit procedural
data-manipulation commands, but as logical statements. The language has
built-in resolution procedures for logical inference.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

